# Redacted environment example

This file shows how to document an incident environment without exposing private data.

```text
Application: OpenClaw
Version: <VERSION>
Operating system: Windows
Runtime: Node.js <VERSION>
Install type: local
Config path: <OPENCLAW_CONFIG>
Session registry: <SESSION_REGISTRY>
Transcript root: <TRANSCRIPT_ROOT>
Backup root: <BACKUP_ROOT>
Host: <HOSTNAME_REDACTED>
User: <USER_REDACTED>
```

## Notes

Replace real values with placeholders before sharing publicly.
